    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jigs4w3D Puzzle Challenge is a casual, relaxing, family-friendly 3D puzzle game. Chill, enjoy the immersive 3D environments and complete a fine selection of your favourite puzzles. Replay value is guaranteed as you can choose from different categories and solve all 31 puzzles on 5 difficulty settings for completely free. If you wish for more, grab your favourite DLC from the store!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>31 free puzzles</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >additional weekly puzzles and updates</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 difficulties for each puzzle</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>2 free, atmospheric environments</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Living Room</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026980/extras/6c2012fd42d2bf6d2f8fe48f47cc5bf7.poster.avif?t=1736875152\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026980/extras/6c2012fd42d2bf6d2f8fe48f47cc5bf7.webm?t=1736875152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026980/extras/6c2012fd42d2bf6d2f8fe48f47cc5bf7.mp4?t=1736875152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cosy Bedroom</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026980/extras/f8a3643117092b4a2d77abf20b3b2e02.poster.avif?t=1736875152\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026980/extras/f8a3643117092b4a2d77abf20b3b2e02.webm?t=1736875152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026980/extras/f8a3643117092b4a2d77abf20b3b2e02.mp4?t=1736875152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>100 achievements</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >additional achievements for future puzzles will be added</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>10 relaxing music tracks</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>enhanced camera movement</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >find small details easily</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026980/extras/ad8cf96efd9ec45449b24a2624cbc96d.poster.avif?t=1736875152\" width=616 height=136 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026980/extras/ad8cf96efd9ec45449b24a2624cbc96d.webm?t=1736875152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026980/extras/ad8cf96efd9ec45449b24a2624cbc96d.mp4?t=1736875152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>made in Unreal Engine 5</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >cozy, realistic, colorful and immersive full 3D environments</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >real-time physics, powered by Chaos Physics<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >light-weight physics simulation solution used in Fortnite</p></li></ul></p></li></ul>",
